{
  "stem": "3040.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to keep these people occupied, and at the same time, humiliate them by giving them some work that they're never accustomed to do.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but this was a short time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lived in Pilzno, actually in Pilzno, it wasn't such a short time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because by the end of 1941 is when they said Pilzno will become [SPEAKING GERMAN], free of Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have to move into a next town, which was Dembitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there, there would be a Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is where all the people living around in this area, Dembitz was one of the larger towns.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of these people have to move into a certain date to a ghetto in Dembitz, which we did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't a suburb, but it was about maybe 50 miles, 40 miles, this is in that area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Became a ghetto in Dembitz, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, over there, this was already you couldn't go live, rent anything to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to move into where you were assigned to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were-- the living quarters were very limited, and people had to join, to share rooms, apartments, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I and my wife lived in this in a house that there were three rooms.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were at least six families in these three rooms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But why, just I and my wife?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just neglected to tell you that my parents-- my in-laws, my wife's parents, her mother died during that incident in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then her father and two sisters, they were all shipped out from Pilzno to another destination that we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most probably to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the only ones to survive that particular incident was my wife and I.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we moved in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came to Dembitz to move into that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
